IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User nico.salas.v
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mailpass.gpg"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/.mail/icloud/Inbox

Channel icloud-inbox
Master :icloud-remote:"INBOX"
Slave :icloud-local:"Inbox"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel icloud-trash
Master :icloud-remote:"Deleted Messages"
Slave :icloud-local:"trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel icloud-sent
Master :icloud-remote:"Sent Messages"
Slave :icloud-local:"sent"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel icloud-archive
Master :icloud-remote:"Archive"
Slave :icloud-local:"archive"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel icloud-drafts
Master :icloud-remote:"Drafts"
Slave :icloud-local:"drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group icloud
Channel icloud-inbox
Channel icloud-sent
Channel icloud-trash
Channel icloud-archive
Channel icloud-drafts